1070
00:44:19,246 --> 00:44:21,145
- Let's eat.
- You're right.

1071
00:44:21,146 --> 00:44:22,146
(They know their manners.)

1072
00:44:23,546 --> 00:44:25,215
- It's good.
- It's delicious.

1073
00:44:25,216 --> 00:44:26,445
- I haven't had it in a while.
- It's good.

1074
00:44:26,446 --> 00:44:27,786
Should I try taking a video?

1075
00:44:28,756 --> 00:44:29,855
- Eun Soo.
- Yes?

1076
00:44:29,856 --> 00:44:31,256
What kind of pizza are you eating?

1077
00:44:31,356 --> 00:44:32,755
Sweet potato.

1078
00:44:32,756 --> 00:44:34,696
Sweet potato pizza. Who bought it for you?

1079
00:44:35,526 --> 00:44:36,856
Potato Teacher.

1080
00:44:37,526 --> 00:44:39,496
- Potato Teacher.
- Yes?

1081
00:44:39,696 --> 00:44:42,165
- Is it good?
- Sweet potato pizza is good.

1082
00:44:42,166 --> 00:44:44,366
- Is it good?
- Yes.

1083
00:44:44,466 --> 00:44:45,865
Kyung Mo, what did you enjoy the most today?

1084
00:44:45,866 --> 00:44:47,706
Acting.

1085
00:44:47,806 --> 00:44:50,075
Was it fun? I'm glad.

1086
00:44:50,076 --> 00:44:51,646
- What about you, Won Jin?
- Scarecrow.

1087
00:44:52,006 --> 00:44:56,345
Ms. Kim had a lot of fun watching you read.

1088
00:44:56,346 --> 00:44:57,646
This is so nice.

1089
00:44:58,246 --> 00:45:00,045
- I want to play a game.
- Me too.

1090
00:45:00,046 --> 00:45:01,416
I have to go to bed right away when I get home.

1091
00:45:01,816 --> 00:45:03,086
Can I play a game in the car?

1092
00:45:03,716 --> 00:45:05,125
Go ahead.

1093
00:45:05,126 --> 00:45:06,525
(He is allowing it.)

1094
00:45:06,526 --> 00:45:07,586
Not in our car.

1095
00:45:07,686 --> 00:45:08,696
Why not?

1096
00:45:09,456 --> 00:45:10,525
Not in our car.

1097
00:45:10,526 --> 00:45:11,596
Why not?

1098
00:45:12,626 --> 00:45:13,895
(Shocked)

1099
00:45:13,896 --> 00:45:15,295
May I go outside?

1100
00:45:15,296 --> 00:45:16,495
Can I go out and play?

1101
00:45:16,496 --> 00:45:18,465
- Go ahead.
- Do you know what she said?

1102
00:45:18,466 --> 00:45:19,736
That sounds like fun.

1103
00:45:20,106 --> 00:45:21,336
Potato Teacher, come with me.

1104
00:45:21,436 --> 00:45:23,205
- I have something to tell you.
- Okay.

1105
00:45:23,206 --> 00:45:24,645
(Hyun Wook is invited.)

1106
00:45:24,646 --> 00:45:26,305
I'll be back.

1107
00:45:26,306 --> 00:45:28,846
- Go ahead.
- Amazing. Holy moly!

1108
00:45:29,146 --> 00:45:31,485
Happy birthday to you

1109
00:45:31,486 --> 00:45:32,486
(Last to leave is Ha Yun.)

1110
00:45:33,586 --> 00:45:35,815
- Whose birthday is it?
- What?

1111
00:45:35,816 --> 00:45:37,556
I was just singing "Happy Birthday."

1112
00:45:37,656 --> 00:45:39,426
It's a cat!

1113
00:45:42,126 --> 00:45:43,196
There are three cats.

1114
00:45:44,696 --> 00:45:46,126
Why did you come back?

1115
00:45:46,566 --> 00:45:47,595
Yes!

1116
00:45:47,596 --> 00:45:48,596
(Quick to close the door)

1117
00:45:50,096 --> 00:45:51,465
(Sighing)

1118
00:45:51,466 --> 00:45:53,466
Come here. I'll teach you.

1119
00:45:55,176 --> 00:45:58,506
I don't mean that I don't want...

1120
00:45:58,606 --> 00:46:00,105
to play with them.

1121
00:46:00,106 --> 00:46:02,075
I'm having fun, and I really mean it.

1122
00:46:02,076 --> 00:46:03,076
They're really great,

1123
00:46:03,446 --> 00:46:05,146
but... How should I put it?

1124
00:46:07,686 --> 00:46:09,416
(Slurping coffee)

1125
00:46:11,826 --> 00:46:13,586
What should I do with Hyun Wook?

1126
00:46:17,526 --> 00:46:18,866
What really makes me mad...

1127
00:46:22,537 --> 00:46:24,237
What should I do with Hyun Wook?

1128
00:46:28,237 --> 00:46:29,577
What really makes me mad...

1129
00:46:31,107 --> 00:46:34,547
is that I have a feeling the kids will like him more than me.

1130
00:46:35,547 --> 00:46:37,177
I can already see it.

1131
00:46:37,917 --> 00:46:40,017
It's going to happen soon.

1132
00:46:40,687 --> 00:46:42,017
I'm the one doing all the hard work,

1133
00:46:42,987 --> 00:46:44,017
then he shows up with some pizza.

1134
00:46:46,227 --> 00:46:49,057
I won't let the kids play games in the car either.

1135
00:46:50,757 --> 00:46:53,167
(She has a strict educational philosophy.)

1136
00:46:54,067 --> 00:46:55,937
I'll tell them to put away their phones.

1137
00:46:56,897 --> 00:46:58,036
He's a funny one.

1138
00:46:58,037 --> 00:47:02,407
(She continued on with her monologue for a while.)

1139
00:47:04,477 --> 00:47:06,147
It's going to be a comfortable ride.

1140
00:47:07,007 --> 00:47:09,817
I want to play with my phone, but I'm not allowed.

1141
00:47:09,947 --> 00:47:13,517
Right. You can't play with it in my car.

1142
00:47:19,257 --> 00:47:22,327
(The ride back home is still fun even without their phones.)

1143
00:47:23,697 --> 00:47:26,727
(It's a party in Tae Ri's car.)

1144
00:47:36,928 --> 00:47:41,228
(Only silence fills Hyun Wook's car.)

1145
00:47:41,328 --> 00:47:43,567
Lotte Giants should have made it to the fall games.

1146
00:47:43,568 --> 00:47:44,598
Yes.

1147
00:47:46,038 --> 00:47:47,508
Don't you want to become a baseball player?

1148
00:47:47,838 --> 00:47:49,607
- What?
- How do you feel about it?

1149
00:47:49,608 --> 00:47:51,538
- Baseball...
- What?

1150
00:47:52,648 --> 00:47:54,078
You were the Tin Man.

1151
00:47:54,108 --> 00:47:55,148
Yes.

1152
00:47:55,448 --> 00:47:56,817
- Was it fun?
- Yes.

1153
00:47:56,818 --> 00:47:58,178
(Asking questions to break the ice)

1154
00:47:59,248 --> 00:48:00,287
You were so good.

1155
00:48:00,288 --> 00:48:01,347
(He never gets discouraged.)

1156
00:48:01,348 --> 00:48:02,888
- Sure.
- What?

1157
00:48:04,858 --> 00:48:06,488
Do you want to ask me anything?

1158
00:48:06,688 --> 00:48:07,727
No.

1159
00:48:07,728 --> 00:48:09,128
- No?
- No.

1160
00:48:10,528 --> 00:48:13,467
- Why not? Take some interest in me.
- Interest?

1161
00:48:13,468 --> 00:48:15,867
- Well?
- It's not like that.

1162
00:48:15,868 --> 00:48:16,967
(Shy)

1163
00:48:16,968 --> 00:48:18,268
But I'm the one...

1164
00:48:18,568 --> 00:48:20,637
- driving you home today.
- Yes.

1165
00:48:20,638 --> 00:48:21,908
(The conversation on the way back home is one-sided.)

1166
00:48:25,038 --> 00:48:26,247
Your bag.

1167
00:48:26,248 --> 00:48:27,908
(They have arrived at Ha Yun's.)

1168
00:48:30,578 --> 00:48:31,578
Let's go.

1169
00:48:31,579 --> 00:48:33,518
(He's already walking.)

1170
00:48:34,518 --> 00:48:36,158
Where is it, Ha Yun?

1171
00:48:40,888 --> 00:48:41,898
Wait for me.

1172
00:48:44,098 --> 00:48:45,127
Wait for me.

1173
00:48:45,128 --> 00:48:47,998
(One-sided love continues.)

1174
00:48:50,998 --> 00:48:52,767
Are you normally this fast at walking?

1175
00:48:52,768 --> 00:48:53,808
No.

1176
00:48:53,868 --> 00:48:54,868
I'm exhausted.

1177
00:48:54,869 --> 00:48:56,308
(I'm exhausted.)

1178
00:48:59,278 --> 00:49:00,577
- Is that a cow?
- Yes.

1179
00:49:00,578 --> 00:49:02,048
(Appearing cows suddenly?)

1180
00:49:03,418 --> 00:49:05,077
That's so cool. Are they yours?

1181
00:49:05,078 --> 00:49:06,117
- Yes.
- Amazing.

1182
00:49:06,118 --> 00:49:07,118
(Their family owns cows.)

1183
00:49:07,688 --> 00:49:09,118
Will they wave back?

1184
00:49:10,758 --> 00:49:11,887
Do they have names?

1185
00:49:11,888 --> 00:49:13,188
- No.
- No?

1186
00:49:14,488 --> 00:49:15,598
Mom!

1187
00:49:17,998 --> 00:49:19,428
- Hello.
- Did you get scolded?

1188
00:49:20,228 --> 00:49:21,527
- Hello.
- Hello.

1189
00:49:21,528 --> 00:49:22,697
(Ha Yun's mom)

1190
00:49:22,698 --> 00:49:24,337
My name is Choi Hyun Wook.

1191
00:49:24,338 --> 00:49:26,467
- Gosh. Nice to meet you.
- Hello.

1192
00:49:26,468 --> 00:49:28,608
(He somehow ended up paying a home visit.)

1193
00:49:28,838 --> 00:49:30,107
Ha Yun attended...

1194
00:49:30,108 --> 00:49:33,147
an outdoor class today. I drove him home.

1195
00:49:33,148 --> 00:49:34,247
Thank you.

1196
00:49:34,248 --> 00:49:36,177
It's dark and cold today. Thank you.

1197
00:49:36,178 --> 00:49:37,277
It was no problem.

1198
00:49:37,278 --> 00:49:38,478
(He sounds like a real teacher.)

1199
00:49:39,348 --> 00:49:40,348
- Did you have a good class?
- Yes.

1200
00:49:40,349 --> 00:49:41,417
Why are you frozen?

1201
00:49:41,418 --> 00:49:42,457
(Staring forward)

1202
00:49:42,458 --> 00:49:44,887
- He seems to be very shy.
- Good job.

1203
00:49:44,888 --> 00:49:47,587
Yes. He can be very shy.

1204
00:49:47,588 --> 00:49:48,627
Yes.

1205
00:49:48,628 --> 00:49:50,927
Please take good care of him.

1206
00:49:50,928 --> 00:49:52,427
What? Okay.

1207
00:49:52,428 --> 00:49:54,368
- I'll do the same.
- Sure.

1208
00:49:54,898 --> 00:49:55,898
(He is asking his mom to take care of him.)

1209
00:49:55,899 --> 00:49:57,297
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

1210
00:49:57,298 --> 00:49:58,338
I'm still new to this.

1211
00:49:58,568 --> 00:50:01,537
He talks a lot about you, although it has only been two days.

1212
00:50:01,538 --> 00:50:02,637
- Really?
- Yes.

1213
00:50:02,638 --> 00:50:04,008
He told me how handsome you were.

1214
00:50:05,038 --> 00:50:06,078
- Really?
- Yes.

1215
00:50:06,578 --> 00:50:07,578
Let's do a high-five.

1216
00:50:09,178 --> 00:50:11,478
(Shy)

1217
00:50:12,148 --> 00:50:15,018
Ha Yun caught my attention the most.

1218
00:50:15,358 --> 00:50:19,088
I guess I could see myself in him.

1219
00:50:19,528 --> 00:50:21,188
(In what way?)

1220
00:50:21,388 --> 00:50:22,697
Can I pass?

1221
00:50:22,698 --> 00:50:25,797
Should we try to help Ha Yun?

1222
00:50:25,798 --> 00:50:28,198
Where should Ha Yun travel to first?

1223
00:50:28,428 --> 00:50:29,498
- Are you okay?
- It brought clouds.

1224
00:50:30,938 --> 00:50:32,437
- Are you shy?
- Yes.

1225
00:50:32,438 --> 00:50:33,708
- Do you feel unconfident?
- Yes.

1226
00:50:35,378 --> 00:50:38,477
He reminded me of myself when I was in elementary school.

1227
00:50:38,478 --> 00:50:40,408
(He was reminded of his own childhood.)

1228
00:50:41,408 --> 00:50:43,417
Let's try it next time when you feel more comfortable.

1229
00:50:43,418 --> 00:50:44,418
- Okay?
- Okay.

1230
00:50:45,688 --> 00:50:48,088
I hope there is another chance...

1231
00:50:48,388 --> 00:50:50,687
for us to talk. Yes.

1232
00:50:50,688 --> 00:50:52,228
(He decided to wait and follow Ha Yun's pace.)

1233
00:50:54,288 --> 00:50:57,698
(After the home visit)

1234
00:51:00,828 --> 00:51:03,338
(He clearly looks tired.)

1235
00:51:06,408 --> 00:51:10,438
(The day feels longer than usual.)

1236
00:51:11,178 --> 00:51:13,008
- Is that you, Hyun Wook?
- Yes.

1237
00:51:13,648 --> 00:51:15,918
- Did you have a safe trip?
- I'm back.

1238
00:51:17,848 --> 00:51:19,048
Good work today.

1239
00:51:19,618 --> 00:51:20,687
When did you get back?

1240
00:51:20,688 --> 00:51:22,288
- Just now. Yes.
- Really?

1241
00:51:23,058 --> 00:51:24,158
Did you have a nice conversation?

1242
00:51:24,658 --> 00:51:25,758
I can't call it a conversation.

1243
00:51:27,428 --> 00:51:29,628
I mostly talked about myself.

1244
00:51:30,328 --> 00:51:32,897
- About you?
- I talked to myself.

1245
00:51:32,898 --> 00:51:34,098
Hyun Wook's monologue.

1246
00:51:35,638 --> 00:51:37,238
A conversation with Hyun Wook.

1247
00:51:37,438 --> 00:51:38,638
It's what you do too.

1248
00:51:39,768 --> 00:51:41,868
- We're similar in that way.
- It's cute.

1249
00:51:42,078 --> 00:51:43,078
Okay.

1250
00:51:43,538 --> 00:51:45,848
Let's do a review later.

1251
00:51:46,908 --> 00:51:48,817
- "Review?" - We need...

1252
00:51:48,818 --> 00:51:50,478
to review today's class.

1253
00:51:57,318 --> 00:52:00,058
Should we do the review and get some rest?

1254
00:52:00,958 --> 00:52:04,427
We have to plan the agenda.

1255
00:52:04,428 --> 00:52:05,998
Can I run tomorrow?

1256
00:52:07,098 --> 00:52:08,228
Go run now.

1257
00:52:11,598 --> 00:52:13,237
I brought...

1258
00:52:13,238 --> 00:52:14,738
more than 20 running outfits,

1259
00:52:15,038 --> 00:52:16,707
but I didn't get to run at all.

1260
00:52:16,708 --> 00:52:18,877
Why did you bring over 20 outfits?

1261
00:52:18,878 --> 00:52:20,648
I thought I'd get to run twice a day.

1262
00:52:21,148 --> 00:52:23,518
You can go for a run now.

1263
00:52:26,348 --> 00:52:28,987
(Happy roommate life)

1264
00:52:28,988 --> 00:52:29,988
What do I wish for?

1265
00:52:30,218 --> 00:52:31,558
It's not much.

1266
00:52:32,628 --> 00:52:34,688
I just want some personal time.

1267
00:52:37,598 --> 00:52:39,597
We could review today's class later.

1268
00:52:39,598 --> 00:52:41,028
(Let's do it next time.)

1269
00:52:41,328 --> 00:52:42,367
Tae Ri!

1270
00:52:42,368 --> 00:52:45,238
(His hidden story)

1271
00:52:46,208 --> 00:52:48,238
(He first appeared with a bright smile.)

1272
00:52:49,338 --> 00:52:52,008
(The first night)

1273
00:52:53,648 --> 00:52:56,878
(He practiced his introduction the moment he arrived.)

1274
00:52:57,418 --> 00:52:59,848
You won't be like this in front of the kids, right?

1275
00:53:00,088 --> 00:53:01,788
I think I might be shy on the first day.

1276
00:53:02,288 --> 00:53:03,288
Really?

1277
00:53:04,458 --> 00:53:07,728
(It doesn't look like we can sleep tonight.)

1278
00:53:09,558 --> 00:53:13,928
(His timid attitude held him back.)

1279
00:53:15,598 --> 00:53:19,068
(On the second day, they prepared the ingredients...)

1280
00:53:20,508 --> 00:53:23,708
(then prepared for class without a break.)

1281
00:53:24,878 --> 00:53:27,408
(Gaunt)

1282
00:53:28,818 --> 00:53:32,448
(He went to bed exhausted every night.)

1283
00:53:34,248 --> 00:53:37,358
I think we both need some time alone.

1284
00:53:37,588 --> 00:53:39,558
But aside from taking a shower or going to the bathroom,

1285
00:53:40,488 --> 00:53:41,528
we hardly had any.

1286
00:53:42,858 --> 00:53:45,127
That's my opinion.

1287
00:53:45,128 --> 00:53:46,998
(Reading her face)

1288
00:53:48,428 --> 00:53:49,637
- But...
- Yes?

1289
00:53:49,638 --> 00:53:51,367
We should definitely do a review.

1290
00:53:51,368 --> 00:53:53,238
- Yes.
- I agree with that.

1291
00:53:54,108 --> 00:53:56,237
- I was quite surprised.
- About what?

1292
00:53:56,238 --> 00:53:57,838
The reading.

1293
00:53:58,878 --> 00:54:01,708
Even if Ju Eun doesn't play the narrator or the Munchkin,

1294
00:54:02,548 --> 00:54:04,248
she should play the witch.

1295
00:54:05,318 --> 00:54:07,388
We should confirm it.

1296
00:54:07,918 --> 00:54:09,887
- I mean it.
- I was so happy.

1297
00:54:09,888 --> 00:54:12,287
Yes. I was so shocked.

1298
00:54:12,288 --> 00:54:14,887
I really wanted to hold onto it.

1299
00:54:14,888 --> 00:54:16,497
I kept on thinking,

1300
00:54:16,498 --> 00:54:18,198
"I wish this could continue."

1301
00:54:18,528 --> 00:54:22,638
But I cannot guarantee we will always feel this way.

1302
00:54:23,298 --> 00:54:25,607
I'm sure of it. They had a lot of fun...

1303
00:54:25,608 --> 00:54:28,367
- because it was a reading.
- Yes.

1304
00:54:28,368 --> 00:54:30,907
- But...
- Once they feel pressured...

1305
00:54:30,908 --> 00:54:32,708
It depends on whether they can memorize it.

1306
00:54:32,878 --> 00:54:35,977
Yes. We should think of a way...

1307
00:54:35,978 --> 00:54:37,348
for them to keep it this way.

1308
00:54:37,448 --> 00:54:38,648
What can we do?

1309
00:54:39,048 --> 00:54:40,347
But this isn't...

1310
00:54:40,348 --> 00:54:42,148
- up to us.
- We need to bring it out.

1311
00:54:42,418 --> 00:54:46,257
It depends on their memory.

1312
00:54:46,258 --> 00:54:48,627
When it comes to memorizing lines,

1313
00:54:48,628 --> 00:54:50,397
as long as they're interested...

1314
00:54:50,398 --> 00:54:53,727
and want to do a good job,

1315
00:54:53,728 --> 00:54:57,437
I think they'll be able to do it.

1316
00:54:57,438 --> 00:54:58,797
- I agree with you.
- Yes.

1317
00:54:58,798 --> 00:55:00,267
- I agree.
- Yes.

1318
00:55:00,268 --> 00:55:03,707
What we need is to help them...

1319
00:55:03,708 --> 00:55:04,737
to focus in the beginning.

1320
00:55:04,738 --> 00:55:07,178
That's why the warming-up time is important.

1321
00:55:07,508 --> 00:55:09,417
- Yes.
- I think it'll be very important.

1322
00:55:09,418 --> 00:55:12,718
I would really like for you to make something.

1323
00:55:13,088 --> 00:55:14,548
- A warm-up?
- Yes.

1324
00:55:15,048 --> 00:55:18,788
If I have free time until class tomorrow,

1325
00:55:19,888 --> 00:55:20,888
I was hoping...

1326
00:55:21,228 --> 00:55:23,457
to drive 10 or 15 minutes away...

1327
00:55:23,458 --> 00:55:25,298
to go for a run.

1328
00:55:27,668 --> 00:55:29,038
Until class?

1329
00:55:29,668 --> 00:55:30,698
What about prepping for class?

1330
00:55:31,238 --> 00:55:32,238
Let's do it now.

1331
00:55:37,738 --> 00:55:38,948
- Hyun Wook.
- Yes?

1332
00:55:39,978 --> 00:55:41,178
I'm...

1333
00:55:42,108 --> 00:55:44,147
It could be more effective.

1334
00:55:44,148 --> 00:55:45,747
- No, no.
- I...

1335
00:55:45,748 --> 00:55:47,288
I don't think so.

1336
00:55:48,118 --> 00:55:49,188
No, no.

1337
00:55:49,558 --> 00:55:51,517
My brain is foggy right now,

1338
00:55:51,518 --> 00:55:55,058
so I don't know how to persuade you.

1339
00:55:55,528 --> 00:55:57,097
I can't think straight.

1340
00:55:57,098 --> 00:55:59,697
But wouldn't we need the time...

1341
00:55:59,698 --> 00:56:01,598
to talk about what to do for the next class?

1342
00:56:01,798 --> 00:56:04,137
We used up everything that was planned until now.

1343
00:56:04,138 --> 00:56:05,567
It's the real deal now.

1344
00:56:05,568 --> 00:56:07,667
We have to come up with a lesson every day.

1345
00:56:07,668 --> 00:56:10,137
You've had it easy until now!

1346
00:56:10,138 --> 00:56:12,948
Do you know how much...

1347
00:56:15,108 --> 00:56:16,518
I'm so scared.

1348
00:56:17,978 --> 00:56:20,247
- Hey!
- I want to go home.

1349
00:56:20,248 --> 00:56:22,048
Do you have any idea...

1350
00:56:22,318 --> 00:56:24,488
(His nose is runny.)

1351
00:56:25,018 --> 00:56:26,528
Did you say I've had it easy?

1352
00:56:26,958 --> 00:56:28,028
Do you know how much...

1353
00:56:28,528 --> 00:56:30,528
I have a lot to say too!

1354
00:56:30,658 --> 00:56:32,867
Do you? Go ahead.

1355
00:56:32,868 --> 00:56:33,927
Spill it.

1356
00:56:33,928 --> 00:56:36,768
(The Mushroom House is on fire.)

1357
00:56:37,238 --> 00:56:39,638
It hasn't been easy for me either.

1358
00:56:40,068 --> 00:56:42,208
Either way...

1359
00:56:42,508 --> 00:56:43,808
Please hear me out this once.

1360
00:56:43,908 --> 00:56:45,907
- Let's say we run out.
- Okay.

1361
00:56:45,908 --> 00:56:48,448
We can talk after class today.

1362
00:56:49,618 --> 00:56:51,778
We can talk after tomorrow's class too.

1363
00:56:52,278 --> 00:56:54,088
Are you saying we shouldn't talk before class?

1364
00:56:54,418 --> 00:56:55,718
Before?

1365
00:56:55,918 --> 00:56:57,287
We can do it 30 minutes before.

1366
00:56:57,288 --> 00:56:58,517
(30 minutes before the class)

1367
00:56:58,518 --> 00:57:00,887
- You said we ran out of ideas.
- Yes.

1368
00:57:00,888 --> 00:57:03,328
- We have to build it from here on.
- Yes.

1369
00:57:03,628 --> 00:57:05,667
- Then...
- So how can we meet less...

1370
00:57:05,668 --> 00:57:08,298
and discuss less than before...

1371
00:57:09,098 --> 00:57:11,338
to build it from here when we have nothing now?

1372
00:57:12,668 --> 00:57:15,877
- We divided our roles.
- Yes.

1373
00:57:15,878 --> 00:57:17,378
- That was what we did.
- Yes.

1374
00:57:18,238 --> 00:57:20,877
I told you to help the students.

1375
00:57:20,878 --> 00:57:22,547
(And Hyun Wook in today's class)

1376
00:57:22,548 --> 00:57:23,878
Back then, I was...

1377
00:57:25,818 --> 00:57:29,188
Nothing you did satisfied me 100 percent.

1378
00:57:30,358 --> 00:57:31,358
Okay.

1379
00:57:31,788 --> 00:57:32,888
Do you admit it?

1380
00:57:33,528 --> 00:57:35,228
If you say so.

1381
00:57:37,628 --> 00:57:39,668
How could I satisfy you 100 percent?

1382
00:57:40,928 --> 00:57:44,968
I didn't prepare it like you did.

1383
00:57:45,438 --> 00:57:48,137
But as for what I needed to do here...

1384
00:57:48,138 --> 00:57:49,438
Like I said yesterday,

1385
00:57:49,978 --> 00:57:52,778
I did what I had to do. It was the same for me today.

1386
00:57:52,878 --> 00:57:56,077
I don't know what it is that you liked or not.

1387
00:57:56,078 --> 00:57:57,677
But that aside,

1388
00:57:57,678 --> 00:57:59,918
I believe I've done my job.

1389
00:58:01,018 --> 00:58:03,617
- I did my best for the kids.
- Right.

1390
00:58:03,618 --> 00:58:04,758
If you...

1391
00:58:05,318 --> 00:58:07,257
didn't like about it, you should say...

1392
00:58:07,258 --> 00:58:09,497
About how you think about them...

1393
00:58:09,498 --> 00:58:11,857
- Yes.
- and how you care for them,

1394
00:58:11,858 --> 00:58:13,467
- I'm on the same page with you.
- Okay.

1395
00:58:13,468 --> 00:58:16,897
But when it comes to the quality of the class...

1396
00:58:16,898 --> 00:58:20,908
or things related to that, I'm saying it was sloppy.

1397
00:58:23,238 --> 00:58:24,908
This is what I think.

1398
00:58:25,338 --> 00:58:28,247
I don't have the slightest intention...

1399
00:58:28,248 --> 00:58:31,448
to doubt or attack the sincerity of Hyun Wook.

1400
00:58:31,778 --> 00:58:34,288
But whether it works or not,

1401
00:58:34,488 --> 00:58:38,488
when you and I give our 100 percent,

1402
00:58:39,258 --> 00:58:44,057
it's obvious it'll change what and how much the kids...

1403
00:58:44,058 --> 00:58:47,828
will get out of this experience.

1404
00:58:48,768 --> 00:58:50,197
In that manner,

1405
00:58:50,198 --> 00:58:51,897
(The reason Tae Ri prepares the class without sleep)

1406
00:58:51,898 --> 00:58:53,667
I want to do more for that.

1407
00:58:53,668 --> 00:58:55,138
Because I do know about it.

1408
00:58:56,778 --> 00:58:58,678
How can I do everything?

1409
00:58:59,608 --> 00:59:01,548
I'm a porter right now.

1410
00:59:02,148 --> 00:59:03,517
It's hurt so much right here...

1411
00:59:03,518 --> 00:59:04,817
since I woke up this morning.

1412
00:59:04,818 --> 00:59:06,848
I need to put on a patch because it sores badly.

1413
00:59:07,518 --> 00:59:11,058
I have to do everything.

1414
00:59:12,418 --> 00:59:15,658
If I have to teach them on top of all those....

1415
00:59:16,658 --> 00:59:18,257
I'm not saying Tae Ri isn't doing anything.

1416
00:59:18,258 --> 00:59:21,297
I'm truly grateful for everything she does.

1417
00:59:21,298 --> 00:59:25,968
But I'm not slacking off here.

1418
00:59:26,238 --> 00:59:27,538
Why am I... Sorry.

1419
00:59:29,408 --> 00:59:33,048
I spoke with such passion all of a sudden.

1420
00:59:33,208 --> 00:59:34,778
It's not that I'm not doing anything.

1421
00:59:35,748 --> 00:59:36,877
What I do in the shadows...

1422
00:59:36,878 --> 00:59:38,047
(The reason Hyun Wook is so upset)

1423
00:59:38,048 --> 00:59:40,117
Does she know how I tried?

1424
00:59:40,118 --> 00:59:41,548
(The reason Hyun Wook is so upset)

1425
00:59:43,558 --> 00:59:45,187
- "Toto is..." - "Toto is..."

1426
00:59:45,188 --> 00:59:46,628
"Dorothy's friend."

1427
00:59:47,128 --> 00:59:51,528
(He went over the kids' lines all throughout the class.)

1428
00:59:53,398 --> 00:59:55,128
Do you have a hand warmer?

1429
00:59:57,338 --> 01:00:00,838
(In case the children get cold,)

1430
01:00:02,408 --> 01:00:05,478
(he diligently took care of them.)

1431
01:00:05,778 --> 01:00:07,548
- Potato Teacher, please help.
- Where are we right now?

1432
01:00:08,648 --> 01:00:09,977
Potato Teacher, can you...

1433
01:00:09,978 --> 01:00:11,118
- Seriously.
- Is it here?

1434
01:00:11,518 --> 01:00:13,948
- Right here.
- "I want to go home."

1435
01:00:14,388 --> 01:00:16,758
"I want to go home."

1436
01:00:17,018 --> 01:00:18,387
Tae Ri, do you want to wear this?

1437
01:00:18,388 --> 01:00:19,588
- What?
- Do you want to wear my jacket?

1438
01:00:19,658 --> 01:00:20,727
- What about you?
- I have this.

1439
01:00:20,728 --> 01:00:22,128
Ms. Kim, it's embarrassing.

1440
01:00:22,758 --> 01:00:24,297
You should drink some water too.

1441
01:00:24,298 --> 01:00:27,928
(He has always put the kids and Ms. Kim before him.)

1442
01:00:29,568 --> 01:00:30,568
(And last night)

1443
01:00:30,569 --> 01:00:31,698
What are you doing?

1444
01:00:32,098 --> 01:00:34,167
- I have a sore throat.
- Do you?

1445
01:00:34,168 --> 01:00:35,367
Does it hurt?

1446
01:00:35,368 --> 01:00:37,808
- Did you take medicine?
- I did after dinner.

1447
01:00:38,578 --> 01:00:40,647
Tae Ri was feeling the symptoms of a cold yesterday,

1448
01:00:40,648 --> 01:00:44,517
so I wanted to make her some tea before she goes to bed.

1449
01:00:44,518 --> 01:00:45,778
But it seemed like she was asleep, so...

1450
01:00:48,418 --> 01:00:51,217
(His caring heart didn't reach her.)

1451
01:00:51,218 --> 01:00:54,527
Does she know how much I care for her?

1452
01:00:54,528 --> 01:00:55,928
In that sense, I'm a bit upset too.

1453
01:01:00,398 --> 01:01:02,168
It does hurt. Really.

1454
01:01:02,968 --> 01:01:04,068
It hurts.

1455
01:01:06,538 --> 01:01:08,608
- Let's take some rest.
- Yes.

1456
01:01:08,708 --> 01:01:09,778
And go to bed.

1457
01:01:23,788 --> 01:01:26,988
(It was a long day in various ways.)

1458
01:01:36,198 --> 01:01:37,838
We had a difference in views.

1459
01:01:38,468 --> 01:01:41,508
I think such a fight can occur when we stay in the same place.

1460
01:01:41,808 --> 01:01:44,778
But one of us will leave the place...

1461
01:01:45,908 --> 01:01:47,048
if we take it further than this.

1462
01:01:48,548 --> 01:01:50,017
I think that might be me.

1463
01:01:50,018 --> 01:01:52,788
(I think that might be me.)

1464
01:01:55,918 --> 01:01:57,887
Gosh. It's tough.

1465
01:01:57,888 --> 01:02:00,128
(Gosh. It's tough.)

1466
01:02:06,768 --> 01:02:11,438
(And next morning)

1467
01:02:18,538 --> 01:02:21,778
(Hyun Wook wakes up.)

1468
01:02:31,318 --> 01:02:35,288
(Tae Ri isn't in her room.)

1469
01:02:39,868 --> 01:02:40,968
Is this real?

1470
01:02:43,168 --> 01:02:44,668
What is this?

1471
01:02:45,898 --> 01:02:47,138
It drove me crazy.

1472
01:02:49,238 --> 01:02:50,238
Yes.

1473
01:02:52,178 --> 01:02:55,548
(Where is Tae Ri?)

1474
01:02:57,878 --> 01:03:00,248
(What? Am I dreaming?)

1475
01:03:02,348 --> 01:03:05,718
(He steps out to the living room in a hurry.)

1476
01:03:18,798 --> 01:03:22,638
(Tae Ri is sleeping in the living room.)

1477
01:03:24,778 --> 01:03:26,778
I went out to the living room,

1478
01:03:27,348 --> 01:03:30,317
and Tae Ri was sleeping in the same state...

1479
01:03:30,318 --> 01:03:32,218
I saw her when we had the argument.

1480
01:03:33,818 --> 01:03:36,458
(Glancing)

1481
01:03:38,188 --> 01:03:41,427
(The traces of the class preparation are still on the desk.)

1482
01:03:41,428 --> 01:03:43,058
(Edit to make it easier.)

1483
01:03:47,068 --> 01:03:48,697
(Tapping)

1484
01:03:48,698 --> 01:03:49,798
Yes?

1485
01:03:50,468 --> 01:03:51,698
Did you sleep here?

1486
01:03:52,338 --> 01:03:53,408
Yes.

1487
01:03:54,538 --> 01:03:55,938
Hyun Wook, what time is it?

1488
01:03:56,578 --> 01:03:58,108
- Right now?
- Yes.

1489
01:04:00,708 --> 01:04:02,008
It's past 9am.

1490
01:04:06,048 --> 01:04:08,148
(Just kidding.)

1491
01:04:10,658 --> 01:04:12,758
I'm dizzy from getting up so fast.

1492
01:04:12,988 --> 01:04:14,488
It's 8:20am right now.

1493
01:04:14,988 --> 01:04:16,358
Tae Ri, your eyes...

1494
01:04:16,598 --> 01:04:19,058
(Bleary)

1495
01:04:20,768 --> 01:04:22,298
When did you go to sleep?

1496
01:04:23,938 --> 01:04:25,638
I don't know. I slept before the sunrise.

1497
01:04:25,868 --> 01:04:27,668
- What?
- I fell asleep before sunrise.

1498
01:04:30,078 --> 01:04:32,638
(It makes him put his hands together politely.)

1499
01:04:34,148 --> 01:04:35,577
I'll wash first.

1500
01:04:35,578 --> 01:04:36,678
(I'll wash first.)

1501
01:04:37,448 --> 01:04:38,578
You can wash first.

1502
01:04:39,418 --> 01:04:41,018
(Excited)

1503
01:04:42,618 --> 01:04:45,358
So many thoughts crossed my mind.

1504
01:04:46,088 --> 01:04:47,158
Tae Ri...

1505
01:04:48,088 --> 01:04:49,228
is really...

1506
01:04:50,528 --> 01:04:51,858
this serious and sincere about it.

1507
01:04:53,668 --> 01:04:57,198
I could really see that she was really putting...

1508
01:04:58,268 --> 01:05:01,938
a lot of thought into how to prepare better classes.

1509
01:05:04,208 --> 01:05:06,207
(She revised the lines the students found difficult...)

1510
01:05:06,208 --> 01:05:07,648
(during the table read.)

1511
01:05:09,048 --> 01:05:12,518
(She tried it herself repeatedly.)

1512
01:05:14,648 --> 01:05:19,188
(She did it deep into the night.)

1513
01:05:22,628 --> 01:05:24,898
(Blinking slowly)

1514
01:05:26,798 --> 01:05:29,598
(Her eyes closed slowly.)

1515
01:05:32,868 --> 01:05:37,178
(And Ms. Kim fell asleep just like that.)

1516
01:05:42,308 --> 01:05:46,848
When I saw Tae Ri sleeping like that in the living room,

1517
01:05:47,318 --> 01:05:48,618
it hurt me.

1518
01:05:49,688 --> 01:05:51,758
It made me look back at myself.

1519
01:05:53,358 --> 01:05:57,028
I thought I should assist her as much as I can by her side.

1520
01:05:58,828 --> 01:06:00,197
So I cooked boiled eggs.

1521
01:06:00,198 --> 01:06:01,567
(Boil eggs...)

1522
01:06:01,568 --> 01:06:03,437
(with a good portion of the egg white gone)

1523
01:06:03,438 --> 01:06:05,268
Nothing is going right. Gosh.

1524
01:06:06,438 --> 01:06:07,508
Coffee too.

1525
01:06:08,438 --> 01:06:10,207
And apples with peanut butter.

1526
01:06:10,208 --> 01:06:12,478
(Apples and peanut butter)

1527
01:06:13,648 --> 01:06:15,307
(What are all these?)

1528
01:06:15,308 --> 01:06:16,318
What do you usually have?

1529
01:06:16,418 --> 01:06:17,617
- Me? For breakfast?
- Yes.

1530
01:06:17,618 --> 01:06:21,188
I have boiled eggs, apples, and peanut butter.

1531
01:06:21,988 --> 01:06:25,788
I've prepared everything she said for breakfast.

1532
01:06:26,558 --> 01:06:27,887
Here's your coffee.

1533
01:06:27,888 --> 01:06:28,987
(Having reflected, Hyun Wook shows his gratitude.)

1534
01:06:28,988 --> 01:06:32,328
I'm sorry. I couldn't peel them well.

1535
01:06:33,398 --> 01:06:35,628
- Try them, though.
- You even peeled them for me.

1536
01:06:39,368 --> 01:06:40,368
Is it all right?

1537
01:06:42,308 --> 01:06:45,338
(Sipping coffee)

1538
01:06:46,508 --> 01:06:49,048
(Totally satisfied)

1539
01:06:53,918 --> 01:06:56,988
I feel very vivid emotions in every moment.

1540
01:06:57,188 --> 01:07:00,927
For example, when Hyun Wook keeps leaving his position...

1541
01:07:00,928 --> 01:07:03,728
or when he can't focus during the class,

1542
01:07:03,828 --> 01:07:06,058
I think I can deal with it in a fun way...

1543
01:07:06,428 --> 01:07:07,428
with an exaggerated sigh and all.

1544
01:07:07,528 --> 01:07:11,238
But when I talk to him in the evening, I get too serious.

1545
01:07:11,868 --> 01:07:13,208
Wait. I'm not wearing a mic.

1546
01:07:13,938 --> 01:07:14,938
Did you hear me okay?

1547
01:07:17,208 --> 01:07:18,477
(Nodding)

1548
01:07:18,478 --> 01:07:20,348
You heard me. Okay.

1549
01:07:22,008 --> 01:07:24,277
I'm upset about those things.

1550
01:07:24,278 --> 01:07:27,318
It makes us look so serious.

1551
01:07:29,888 --> 01:07:31,417
(She's more upset than anyone because they keep arguing.)

1552
01:07:31,418 --> 01:07:33,188
We can really make it happen.

1553
01:07:33,388 --> 01:07:37,028
I really want this to be fun.

1554
01:07:38,998 --> 01:07:42,527
In order to do that, we need something exciting.

1555
01:07:42,528 --> 01:07:45,038
(What Ms. Kim needs right now is something exciting.)

1556
01:07:45,768 --> 01:07:48,608
(Exciting trips)

1557
01:07:49,638 --> 01:07:52,138
(Exciting running)

1558
01:07:52,978 --> 01:07:55,608
(Exciting classes)

1559
01:07:56,918 --> 01:07:59,348
(They smile while thinking about the kids.)

1560
01:08:00,018 --> 01:08:02,288
(What these inexperienced teachers can think of is their students.)

1561
01:08:03,358 --> 01:08:06,188
(But they made the cry.)

1562
01:08:06,958 --> 01:08:09,488
(What happened in the theater class?)

1563
01:08:09,728 --> 01:08:12,028
Gosh. This is so hard.

1564
01:08:15,342 --> 01:08:17,342
Dramaday.me
